17
00:02:26,680 --> 00:02:29,639
Make him feel he's still a normal person.

18
00:02:33,800 --> 00:02:34,520
Well...

19
00:02:34,520 --> 00:02:36,439
Then you gotta tell those two brothers.

20
00:02:37,560 --> 00:02:38,439
Talking about those two.

21
00:02:38,439 --> 00:02:40,439
This one's hiding from trouble, right?

22
00:02:40,439 --> 00:02:42,000
And the other says he's busy.

23
00:02:42,479 --> 00:02:43,879
Spoiled rotten.

24
00:02:44,520 --> 00:02:45,960
When you lecture me,

25
00:02:45,960 --> 00:02:47,240
