26
00:02:47,240 --> 00:02:49,240
But when trouble lands on *their* heads,

27
00:02:50,240 --> 00:02:51,439
They're useless.

28
00:02:52,080 --> 00:02:54,240
Every single one, they just can't handle it.

29
00:02:54,240 --> 00:02:55,400
They just need a good beating.

30
00:02:56,120 --> 00:02:59,240
