31
00:03:00,719 --> 00:03:01,759
Same as before.

32
00:03:02,680 --> 00:03:03,960
If there's really no other way,

33
00:03:04,000 --> 00:03:05,840
then we'll do it my way.

34
00:03:12,719 --> 00:03:14,000
Tomorrow at noon,

35
00:03:14,680 --> 00:03:16,400
everyone meet at Weiguo's place.

36
00:03:20,919 --> 00:03:22,240
Anyone who doesn't show up...

37
00:03:22,240 --> 00:03:23,840
