38
00:03:25,159 --> 00:03:25,960
Hey, hey...

39
00:03:26,240 --> 00:03:27,520
Don't be hasty.

40
00:03:44,759 --> 00:03:45,560
Big Brother.

41
00:03:45,800 --> 00:03:46,439
Alright.

42
00:03:48,280 --> 00:03:50,439
