58
00:04:24,959 --> 00:04:27,240
And I'll do it my way.

59
00:04:31,600 --> 00:04:32,600
Big Bro, I...

60
00:04:32,720 --> 00:04:33,199
Shut your mouth!

61
00:04:33,199 --> 00:04:34,279
It's not your turn yet.

62
00:04:34,720 --> 00:04:35,839
Second Brother, get over here.

63
00:04:37,600 --> 00:04:38,480
What for?

64
00:04:38,480 --> 00:04:40,399
