73
00:04:56,839 --> 00:04:57,399
Yes.

74
00:04:57,600 --> 00:04:58,480
You, come here.

75
00:05:11,360 --> 00:05:12,360
Sit your ass down there.

76
00:05:15,680 --> 00:05:16,600
Big Bro, actually...

77
00:05:16,600 --> 00:05:17,720
Not your turn yet!

78
00:05:17,920 --> 00:05:19,120
You shut your mouth!

79
00:05:19,480 --> 00:05:20,600
Qiu'er, you come here.

80
00:05:24,160 --> 00:05:25,720
Know why I'm hitting you?

81
00:05:26,920 --> 00:05:27,600
Yes.

82
00:05:28,959 --> 00:05:30,639
Xiao Jia bullied you.

83
00:05:31,000 --> 00:05:32,759
And all you know is how to hide.

84
00:05:33,839 --> 00:05:35,360
You hide from your mom.

85
00:05:35,360 --> 00:05:36,800
You hide from your wife.

86
00:05:36,800 --> 00:05:38,480
Where else you gonna hide?

87
00:05:38,480 --> 00:05:39,399
Get over here!

88
00:05:47,199 --> 00:05:48,360
Go sit over there.

89
00:05:51,879 --> 00:05:53,160
Weiguo, you get over here.

90
00:05:53,160 --> 00:05:54,279
Bro, how about...

91
00:05:55,279 --> 00:05:56,680
I take the beating for Weiguo.

92
00:05:56,959 --> 00:05:58,560
