95
00:06:04,759 --> 00:06:05,519
Come here.

96
00:06:06,680 --> 00:06:08,480
Big Bro, I don't need it.

97
00:06:08,480 --> 00:06:09,240
I'm fine.

98
00:06:09,399 --> 00:06:11,959
