101
00:06:15,720 --> 00:06:17,120
I've decided to have the surgery.

102
00:06:21,360 --> 00:06:22,120
Really.

103
00:06:24,160 --> 00:06:25,920
I wanted to tell you as soon as you walked in,

104
00:06:26,160 --> 00:06:27,600
but you didn't give me a chance.

105
00:06:27,600 --> 00:06:28,759
You just started hitting people.

106
00:06:34,360 --> 00:06:36,360
You just needed a good whack, you know that?

107
00:06:36,560 --> 00:06:37,600
Big Bro, I was wrong.

108
00:06:39,040 --> 00:06:39,839
I admit it.

109
00:06:41,040 --> 00:06:43,519
Lately, my emotions have been all over the place.

110
00:06:45,040 --> 00:06:46,279
But I've really made up my mind.

111
00:06:46,279 --> 00:06:47,240
I'm fully determined.

112
00:06:47,240 --> 00:06:48,319
I'm going to have this surgery.

113
00:06:49,040 --> 00:06:50,560
I just haven't had the chance yet

114
00:06:50,560 --> 00:06:51,879
