115
00:06:52,800 --> 00:06:53,839
Really, I've decided.

116
00:06:53,839 --> 00:06:54,759
Don't be angry anymore.

117
00:06:55,120 --> 00:06:55,920
Okay?

118
00:06:59,279 --> 00:07:01,120
Let's focus on the surgery.

119
00:07:01,360 --> 00:07:02,600
It's okay, Big Bro.

120
00:07:09,839 --> 00:07:10,639
Alright then.

121
00:07:10,920 --> 00:07:12,240
Sit down, sit, just sit first.

122
00:07:12,240 --> 00:07:13,399
You sit down too.

123
00:07:16,600 --> 00:07:17,360
Second Brother.

124
00:07:17,920 --> 00:07:18,720
Third Brother.

125
00:07:19,600 --> 00:07:20,800
And me, your Big Brother.

126
00:07:21,240 --> 00:07:22,480
Qiu'er is our brother.

127
00:07:22,680 --> 00:07:24,360
He's been bullied.

128
00:07:24,360 --> 00:07:25,399
What should we do?

129
00:07:27,160 --> 00:07:28,160
We deal with him.

130
00:07:28,600 --> 00:07:29,839
Let's go deal with him!

131
00:07:29,839 --> 00:07:30,600
Let's go, go!

132
00:07:30,600 --> 00:07:32,279
Qiu'er, you watch from the side. Let's go!

133
00:07:32,639 --> 00:07:33,279
Go!

134
00:08:04,959 --> 00:08:06,279
Where are you brothers off to?

135
00:08:19,040 --> 00:08:21,240
You saw how pathetic Tong Qiu looked, right?

136
00:08:28,279 --> 00:08:30,399
Hello, last four digits of your phone?

137
00:08:30,399 --> 00:08:31,279
6066.

138
00:08:31,279 --> 00:08:32,879
Okay, please fasten your seatbelt.

139
00:09:09,200 --> 00:09:09,840
Bro.

140
00:09:10,399 --> 00:09:12,159
I'll go in alone. I can handle it.

141
00:09:13,559 --> 00:09:14,200
Okay?

142
00:09:15,559 --> 00:09:16,440
No problem.

143
00:09:26,440 --> 00:09:27,320
Jia Zhilong

144
00:09:31,679 --> 00:09:32,440
What do you want?

145
00:09:32,840 --> 00:09:33,840
Following me?

146
00:09:35,279 --> 00:09:36,480
I want to have a proper talk with you.

147
00:09:36,559 --> 00:09:38,080
What do we have to talk about?

148
00:09:39,879 --> 00:09:42,159
I know it was you who reported me, right?

149
00:09:42,440 --> 00:09:44,159
Can you go to the bank and explain

150
00:09:44,159 --> 00:09:46,039
this matter clearly to everyone?

151
00:09:46,440 --> 00:09:47,840
If you do that, then we can

152
00:09:48,159 --> 00:09:49,440
let bygones be bygones, okay?

153
00:09:51,320 --> 00:09:52,519
Let bygones be bygones?

154
00:09:53,679 --> 00:09:55,159
Can't make it out there anymore, huh?

155
00:09:55,200 --> 00:09:56,279
Want to come back to the bank?

156
00:09:57,039 --> 00:09:57,559
Fine.

157
00:09:58,320 --> 00:09:59,120
Beg me.

158
00:09:59,799 --> 00:10:01,399
My word carries weight at the bank now.

159
00:10:01,399 --> 00:10:02,759
You beg me to put in a good word for you.

160
00:10:05,240 --> 00:10:06,279
Not convinced, are you?

161
00:10:07,080 --> 00:10:08,080
Alright, hit me.

162
00:10:10,039 --> 00:10:10,799
I don't dare.

163
00:10:12,159 --> 00:10:13,559
It's so simple.

164
00:10:13,559 --> 00:10:15,120
Either you beat me up,

165
00:10:15,399 --> 00:10:16,519
or you beg me.

166
00:10:19,039 --> 00:10:19,840
Qiu'er.

167
00:10:21,039 --> 00:10:22,799
*You're* the one talking about letting bygones be bygones?

168
00:10:24,519 --> 00:10:25,159
Here.

169
00:10:28,159 --> 00:10:29,399
This video is you, right?

170
00:10:30,320 --> 00:10:31,639
I'm not wronging you, am I?

171
00:10:32,919 --> 00:10:34,360
*You* want to let bygones be bygones with *me*?

172
00:10:37,639 --> 00:10:38,639
Beg me.

173
00:10:44,720 --> 00:10:46,200
Beg me.

174
00:10:50,519 --> 00:10:52,120
You beg me to delete this video,

175
00:10:52,639 --> 00:10:54,720
and then I'll go plead for you at the bank.

176
00:11:02,039 --> 00:11:03,440
Acting like a jerk, are you?

177
00:11:08,039 --> 00:11:09,559
Qiu'er, are you insane?

178
00:11:09,639 --> 00:11:10,919
You believe I'll call the police?

179
00:11:10,919 --> 00:11:11,799
Go ahead, call them.

180
00:11:11,799 --> 00:11:12,639
Call them.

181
00:11:12,639 --> 00:11:13,799
Hurry up and call.

182
00:11:13,799 --> 00:11:14,679
No phone, huh?

183
00:11:14,679 --> 00:11:15,559
Use mine to call.

184
00:11:15,639 --> 00:11:17,320
Here, use mine to call.

185
00:11:18,159 --> 00:11:19,799
Explain everything clearly to the police.

186
00:11:19,799 --> 00:11:21,399
Tell them exactly what's going on between us.

187
00:11:21,399 --> 00:11:22,440
Do you think I want to go back to that bank?

188
00:11:22,440 --> 00:11:24,159
Let me tell you, I'm not going back!

189
00:11:24,159 --> 00:11:25,919
Come on, I'm telling you to call! Call!

190
00:11:25,919 --> 00:11:26,679
No matter what,

191
00:11:26,679 --> 00:11:27,440
no matter what it takes,

192
00:11:27,440 --> 00:11:28,799
I have to let everyone know everything.

193
00:11:28,799 --> 00:11:29,159
Let me tell you,

194
00:11:29,159 --> 00:11:30,440
