196
00:11:31,679 --> 00:11:32,559
Call, hurry up!

197
00:11:32,559 --> 00:11:34,399
Call, call, call!

198
00:11:41,399 --> 00:11:42,440
I don't dare.

199
00:11:43,559 --> 00:11:44,639
I don't dare.

200
00:11:47,919 --> 00:11:49,960
