203
00:11:53,679 --> 00:11:55,000
You just had to push your luck, didn't you?

204
00:11:55,000 --> 00:11:56,039
Now you don't dare.

205
00:11:56,279 --> 00:11:57,679
Afraid everyone will find out.

206
00:11:58,759 --> 00:12:00,559
Alright, no problem.

207
00:12:00,559 --> 00:12:01,559
I'm telling you,

208
00:12:01,799 --> 00:12:03,039
I'll go investigate and gather evidence.

209
00:12:03,039 --> 00:12:04,679
I will definitely submit this defense material.

210
00:12:04,679 --> 00:12:05,879
I'll find all the evidence.

211
00:12:05,879 --> 00:12:07,159
Then you can figure out what to do.

212
00:12:10,159 --> 00:12:11,519
I'll buy you three phones.

213
00:12:18,440 --> 00:12:20,000
What are you doing?

214
00:12:20,279 --> 00:12:22,159
You think it's easy for me, don't you?

215
00:12:33,399 --> 00:12:34,320
It's settled.

216
00:12:35,399 --> 00:12:36,399
I'm heading out first.

217
00:12:37,039 --> 00:12:38,000
Where are you going?

218
00:12:39,639 --> 00:12:40,679
To find Xiaoshi.

219
00:12:43,519 --> 00:12:44,879
This guy.

220
00:14:13,440 --> 00:14:14,679
Leaving, huh?

221
00:14:30,279 --> 00:14:32,399
Maybe you think I can't see reality clearly,

222
00:14:37,279 --> 00:14:39,519
