226
00:14:52,720 --> 00:14:53,519
Honey.

227
00:14:54,639 --> 00:14:57,120
I know I've let you down a lot over the years.

228
00:14:58,840 --> 00:15:00,039
I always hide in my own

229
00:15:00,039 --> 00:15:01,559
comfort zone.

230
00:15:01,720 --> 00:15:03,639
When I encounter problems, I hide.

231
00:15:03,639 --> 00:15:05,519
I hide from problems.

232
00:15:05,519 --> 00:15:08,120
Hiding became a habit for me.

233
00:15:09,000 --> 00:15:10,159
You got used to it.

234
00:15:11,039 --> 00:15:12,720
Everyone got used to it.

235
00:15:14,240 --> 00:15:15,679
Sometimes, you know,

236
00:15:17,120 --> 00:15:18,240
when I get drunk

237
00:15:20,000 --> 00:15:21,519
and wake up the next morning,

238
00:15:21,519 --> 00:15:23,000
I feel like

239
00:15:26,519 --> 00:15:27,919
by hiding and hiding,

240
00:15:28,799 --> 00:15:30,799
I'm about to hide even my comfort zone away.

241
00:15:32,679 --> 00:15:33,720
So I just

242
00:15:34,600 --> 00:15:35,639
lie flat.

243
00:15:39,120 --> 00:15:41,879
I become a pile of mud,

244
00:15:42,039 --> 00:15:43,159
letting people shape me however they want.

245
00:15:43,159 --> 00:15:45,159
Whatever shape they mold me into, that's what I am.

246
00:15:45,360 --> 00:15:47,120
And I'm okay with it.

247
00:15:49,799 --> 00:15:50,799
But after being molded and molded,

248
00:15:50,799 --> 00:15:52,879
I forgot what I used to be like.

249
00:15:52,879 --> 00:15:54,759
I even forgot what I should be like now.

250
00:15:54,759 --> 00:15:55,879
What should I be like?

251
00:15:56,000 --> 00:15:57,879
Tell me, what should I be like?

252
00:16:00,720 --> 00:16:02,480
But I want to thank Big Brother.

253
00:16:04,600 --> 00:16:05,960
I want to thank you.

254
00:16:07,639 --> 00:16:09,559
And I want to thank our baby.

255
00:16:11,000 --> 00:16:12,120
It's you who made me realize

256
00:16:12,120 --> 00:16:13,720
it's time for me to be strong.

257
00:16:14,120 --> 00:16:15,399
It's time for me to change.

258
00:16:15,480 --> 00:16:16,600
It's time for me to have responsibility.

259
00:16:16,600 --> 00:16:18,480
Because I'm a father now.

260
00:16:19,200 --> 00:16:20,879
I'm a father now.

261
00:16:22,639 --> 00:16:24,240
Wife, believe in me one more time.

262
00:16:24,559 --> 00:16:26,200
This time, I will definitely do it myself.

263
00:16:26,200 --> 00:16:27,679
I'll personally mold myself,

264
00:16:27,679 --> 00:16:28,559
even if in the end I'm molded

265
00:16:28,559 --> 00:16:30,159
into a broken basin,

266
00:16:30,159 --> 00:16:31,840
like a broken gourd,

267
00:16:32,360 --> 00:16:34,440
I think I'll still have my own value.

268
00:16:34,440 --> 00:16:36,600
I'll have my own proper shape, and I accept it.

269
00:16:39,480 --> 00:16:41,000
I can't hide anymore.

270
00:16:41,600 --> 00:16:43,480
I absolutely will not hide anymore.

271
00:16:45,720 --> 00:16:46,879
In the past, I would

272
00:16:47,720 --> 00:16:49,919
always feel tired,

273
00:16:51,080 --> 00:16:52,200
want to escape,

274
00:16:53,279 --> 00:16:54,720
not want to go on.

275
00:16:57,480 --> 00:16:59,759
So I wanted everyone to wait a bit longer.

276
00:17:01,240 --> 00:17:02,440
For you to wait.

277
00:17:04,200 --> 00:17:05,480
For myself to wait.

278
00:17:07,400 --> 00:17:08,319
But this time,

279
00:17:11,079 --> 00:17:12,599
